column5: Nakina North had a cancellation. June 23-30, Percy Lake. A good sized lake with pike and walleye and miles of navigable river downstream with brookÂ trout. I am going in August. $650 CAD plus hst for min party of 4. https://www.nakinanorthoutfitters.ca/percy-lake/
Short notice but a smoking good deal! This is one of the top lakes in Ontario imo. It fishes great all season but this week would be prime time for numbers.
sheesh---wish i could take advantage of that!
